px-House_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/60px-House_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Blackwood.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Blackwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/15px-House_Blackwood.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/23px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/30px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">House Blackwood</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Blackwood.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Blackwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/15px-House_Blackwood.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/23px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/30px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Blackwood\" title=\"Tytos Blackwood\">Tytos Blackwood</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Westermen garrison</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Army of House Blackwood</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>liberation of Raventree Hall</b> occurs after the coronation of <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.\n</p><p>With the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Camps\" title=\"Battle of the Camps\">Battle of the Camps</a> saving <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> army besieging it, King Robb gives the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlords</a> leave to liberate their own seats and lands from Lannister occupation. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Blackwood\" title=\"Tytos Blackwood\">Tytos Blackwood</a> leaves Riverrun with the intent to recover <a href=\"/index.php/Raventree_Hall\" title=\"Raventree Hall\">Raventree Hall</a>, which had been <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_Raventree_Hall\" title=\"Fall of Raventree Hall\">seized</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> and was occupied by a Lannister garrison. Tytos is successful but his lands have been despoiled by the occupiers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=